FLORIDA BOARD OF BAR EXAMINERS RE: K.V.B. CASE NO.: SC18-679 Supreme Court of Florida. MAY 9, 2018

A True Copy

John A. Tomasino

Clerk, Supreme Court

The Joint Stipulation to Extend Probation is approved and the probationary period imposed against K.V.B. in Florida Board of Bar Examiners Re: K.V.B. , 177 So.3d 607 (Fla. 2015), is extended until May 9, 2023, under the existing terms and conditions with the added conditions that K.V.B. immediately obtain an AA sponsor and do the step work involved in the AA program, effective immediately.

The filing of a motion for rehearing shall not alter the effective date of this probation.
